    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>An Inconvenient Woman</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Marsha Peruo letter takes exception to prejudice shown toward Pfc Barry Winchell by his friends in David France's May 28 article on Winchell's murder</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I was appalled by the extreme prejudice shown toward Barry Winchell by his ''friends.'' I was also amazed at how much excessive drinking was tolerated by the military. It sounded to me as if alcohol abuse was as much to blame for the murder as was hatred of gays.</p>
        <p>Marsha Peruo</p>
        <p>New York</p>
      </block>
